GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 20th March, 2024
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from 20th March, 2024:
Shri Pashu Pati Kumar Paras relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of
Food Processing Industries.
Shri Kiren Rijiju assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Food Processing
Industries. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of Earth
Sciences.
